{"tid":1297574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家都玩夠了","createTime":"2019-07-08T16:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:21:23.000Z","uid":30408,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a4053e2d8fe33f8c394bcf8cabf3f224642f9485","tid":1297574,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"明白有人話想做啲嘢放鬆下<br />\n但奈何依家連登比外界推得太過重要<br />\n各界既人都會經連登留意動態發展<br />\n所以依啲事情等成功咗再圍爐玩啦<br />\n呼籲大家見到新聞或者主流post可以推咗先<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首要係洗返走曬啲post</span></span><br />\n 等有啲巴打唔會以為有事<br />\n利申依個月既大部分都有出好明白聽到XX要人<br />\n個種心驚膽戰既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家握個手 唔好內戰<br />\n槍口對外 對我都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但唔好再嘈交<br />\n有巴打中伏既話講聲對唔住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對唔住</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1ca6b937d88d6cfb3d1d6fa2333472549cb02fb","tid":1297574,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:04:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82b39ed4734ec42396422a1635174d13f883f2ee","tid":1297574,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:04:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12b3f5201c7987fc2bc2b31983dee28e68b0c6d4","tid":1297574,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:05:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3418efa064e86eb38534519c8b9d045e0a6ee6d8","tid":1297574,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52f87d4af6d8cae0094e4d276dfc0e911ae23993","tid":1297574,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"381efbf18dd0165d8f38728ccee94a2b0112bd17","tid":1297574,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:06:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fd854b410711a6b664d97b8c3065756841a6f2c","tid":1297574,"uid":30408